data.description: Location-Location-Location – Here’s a Cape Cod style home just waiting for new owners! Close to more attractions than you can count. The home sets on 1.34 acres and offers up to 5 bedrooms with 3 on the main floor. 2 full baths and 2 half, first floor laundry, large living room with wood burning fireplace, nice open kitchen and more. The master suite has its own full bath and 2 large walk-in closets plus access to the back patio. The other two bedrooms share a jack & jill full bath. The 2 large rooms upstairs, one with a half bath, can be 2 additional bedrooms. This home features solid 6 panel oak doors. A full dry basement gives you lots of storage and includes a shower. Utilities are all electric. This home includes 2692 SF, a fully screened back porch and evening sunset views you will surely enjoy!
